snippet.title: Digimon Emerald Project COMPLETED Rom Hack - Full DigiDex (350+ Digimon)
snippet.description:
Digimon Emerald Project is now officially complete! This is the definitive version with 352 obtainable Digimon, all with custom stats, movepools, abilities, etc.

-FEATURES-
-350+ new monsters with unique stats, abilities, Typing, and movepools built from the ground-up
-As many as five or even six stages for prominent Digimon
-Custom moves from the Digimon canon (Every single Digimon has its signature attack)
-Digidex Entries state criteria for evolution
-EV/IV Checker, Up to Gen VII Abilities and Moves, Reusable TMs, Fairy Type, Physical-Special Split, Poison Survival, BW Repel System, etc.

Download link:
https://www.pokecommunity.com/showthread.php?t=467949
